{"tid":1085152,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"好憎自己，鬧走女朋友","createTime":"2019-03-31T03:12:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-31T09:30:43.000Z","uid":104555,"like":1,"dislike":23,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"4942c6674c6ffc845052a3d1dc4c606727a78f2c","tid":1085152,"uid":104555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T03:12:06.000Z","msg":"女朋友好溫柔，好錫我<br />\n完全係我想要既女仔<br />\n我錫到佢燶，佢又好愛我<br />\n一齊咁耐所有回憶都係好美好，好甜蜜<br />\n<br />\n呢排好多事煩，個心好亂、好躁底、好大壓力<br />\n佢都盡力安撫我既情緒<br />\n但我仍然口快講左句粗口（真係好想死）<br />\n<br />\n只係短短一星期時間<br />\n就摧毀左我地咁耐建立既關係<br />\n而加望住佢d相，滿淚盈眶<br />\n好後悔自己一嬲把口就失控<br />\n<br />\n好想好想同番佢一齊<br />\n但唔想害人<br />\n<br />\n有無人明？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n奉勸各位巴打真係要珍惜自己女朋友<br />\n唔好步我呢件垃圾既後塵"},{"pid":"24c83a43d505b133ebb25b077bbf7ad9e1cfe2e9","tid":1085152,"uid":200587,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T03:13:43.000Z","msg":"講左一句粗口佢就走？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"254e7122b0c6280da4385d8f592248291224ab1c","tid":1085152,"uid":104555,"like":1,"dislike":9,"score":-8,"quote":{"pid":"24c83a43d505b133ebb25b077bbf7ad9e1cfe2e9","tid":1085152,"uid":200587,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T03:13:43.000Z","msg":"講左一句粗口佢就走？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T03:15:00.000Z","msg":"唔係，而係嘈交時講左粗口<br />\n佢覺得好失望<br />\n因為我平時一句大聲對佢都唔會"},{"pid":"98048412ab3290967f3dcdd4a1cfe9e6ecec942e","tid":1085152,"uid":104555,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T03:17:17.000Z","msg":"一星期前有講有笑<br />\n而加身邊已經失去左佢<br />\n望住d相，佢既笑容、佢既溫柔<br />\n真係好想死"},{"pid":"b8c8577f746f8637379a9c41fbb1a0b300e3fee8","tid":1085152,"uid":106296,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T03:19:30.000Z","msg":"氹返佢囉<br />\n雖然我覺得佢都誇張 嘈一次交惡少少就走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n成世人流流長有咩可能唔嘈交唔發癲？"},{"pid":"91d6987540f24a764f1cfbbcc8c2925828cc8c78","tid":1085152,"uid":104555,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"b8c8577f746f8637379a9c41fbb1a0b300e3fee8","tid":1085152,"uid":106296,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T03:19:30.000Z","msg":"氹返佢囉<br />\n雖然我覺得佢都誇張 嘈一次交惡少少就走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n成世人流流長有咩可能唔嘈交唔發癲？"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T03:22:00.000Z","msg":"「我的作風老土，但我始終覺得做人要公道。和你一齊由相識到現在，無論怎樣，我都會記住你的恩情。我不想長篇大論，我只想話我這段時間是過的有意義，你確實讓我感受到喜樂和支持，我會記得大家的好，戴著你的祝褔繼續往前走。你有個善良的心腸，願你平安和福氣。最後，希望我們能做遠方的朋友，為對方祝褔。感謝我能與你相遇，珍重。」<br />\n<br />\n嘈到咁，會有得救？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fcda06f625207fd6307a62c03428fef35f5041c3","tid":1085152,"uid":200587,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"254e7122b0c6280da4385d8f592248291224ab1c","tid":1085152,"uid":104555,"like":1,"dislike":9,"score":-8,"quote":{"pid":"24c83a43d505b133ebb25b077bbf7ad9e1cfe2e9","tid":1085152,"uid":200587,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T03:13:43.000Z","msg":"講左一句粗口佢就走？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T03:15:00.000Z","msg":"唔係，而係嘈交時講左粗口<br />\n佢覺得好失望<br />\n因為我平時一句大聲對佢都唔會"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T03:22:09.000Z","msg":"係人嬲都想發洩一下<br />\n講句粗口都係想抒壓<br />\n如果你女朋友識諗應該會理解到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咪試下同佢道歉 解釋番<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e7ef677fc4e6d8a16a8c53be7741917b1f6f346","tid":1085152,"uid":106296,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T03:23:13.000Z","msg":"耶撚？"},{"pid":"9b454909e295f38ed97fb16bb599fef9808bbf39","tid":1085152,"uid":200587,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":